1:03:14.073 --> 1:03:18.978
Brother C.T. Russell
first visited Austria in 1891. 


1:03:18.978 --> 1:03:21.246
He returned in 1911 to plant


1:03:21.247 --> 1:03:25.619
further seeds of Kingdom truth 
in the capital city, Vienna. 


1:03:25.618 --> 1:03:29.455
Today, there are more than 21,000
active publishers


1:03:29.455 --> 1:03:33.058
among the eight million
who live in Austria.


1:03:33.058 --> 1:03:35.861
One of the 301 congregations


1:03:35.862 --> 1:03:39.032
is the German-language congregation
in Uderns. 


1:03:39.032 --> 1:03:44.070
